<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="clap-v">clap <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /klæp/    美 /klæp/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1vi-vt">1.<strong>vi &amp; vt 为…鼓掌；拍手：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As the president ended his speech, we clapped politely.
校长演讲完毕，我们礼貌地鼓掌。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They were <strong>clapping their hands</strong> to the music.
他们随着音乐的节奏拍起手来。</p></div></div>